==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hit man
<hw>hit man</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A professional murderer,
esp. one working for a criminal organization; also called
<altname>torpedo</altname>.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A slanderer working for political purposes to damage
the reputation of an opponent; a <er>hatchet man</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>hit on</ent>⟦br⟧
